  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK245">
<l>alla laruḷāḷvārk killai vaḷivaḻaṅku</l>
<l>mallaṉmā ñālam kari</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This great rich earth over which the wind blows, is a witness that sorrow never comes upon the kind-hearted.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
